################ Slotted ALOHA ##################

File:           slotted_aloha.py
Example Usage:  python slotted_aloha.py -n 50 -w 2 -p 0.02 -m 4000 -v -r
Arguments:      -n  number of nodes
                -w  initial value of collision window
                -p  packet generation rate
                -m  maximum number of packets to be transmitted
                -v  activates verbose mode
                -r  if enabled, the program quits if number of retransmissions for a particular packet exceeds 10

Running the script

